-- Drought in Lower 48 States Expands in Week, U.S. Monitor Says
-- B y   J o e   R i c h t e r
-- 2012-08-23T12:48:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-23/drought-in-lower-48-states-expands-in-week-u-s-monitor-says.html
The drought in the lower 48 states
expanded to 63.2 percent in the week ended Aug. 21 from 61.77
percent a week earlier, the U.S. Drought Monitor said today on
its website.  The most severe level of drought, called exceptional, rose
to 6.31 percent from 6.26 percent.  To contact the reporter on this story:
